(ns farsund.login.ui
  (:require [cljs.spec.alpha :as s]
            [reagent.core :as r]
            [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [oops.core :refer [oget oget+]]
            [mui.core :as mui]
            [mui.colors :as colors]
            [farsund.flex :as flex]
            [farsund.utils.core :as u]
            [farsund.utils.key :as k]


            ["@material-ui/icons/Menu" :default MenuIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/AccountCircle" :default AccountCircle]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Email" :default Email]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Lock" :default Lock]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Visibility" :default Visibility]
            ["@material-ui/icons/VisibilityOff" :default VisibilityOff]
            ["mdi-material-ui/FacebookBox" :default FacebookBox]
            ["mdi-material-ui/Google" :default Google]
            ["chroma-js" :as chroma]))


(defn login-button []
  (let [user (rf/subscribe [:user/get])]
    (fn []
      (if @user
        [flex/box {:width  48
                   :height 48}
         [mui/avatar {:alt      (:display-name @user)
                      :src      (:photo-url @user)
                      :on-click #(rf/dispatch [:ui/set-panel :user-menu])
                      :style    {
                                 :width  32
                                 :height 32
                                 :margin 8
                                 }}]]
        [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:turn-on [[:login :show-dialog?]]])}
         [:> AccountCircle]]))))


(defn login-dialog []
  (let [theme (rf/subscribe [:theme/get])
        open? (rf/subscribe [:login/show-dialog?])
        text-secondary (rf/subscribe [:theme/get :palette :text :secondary])
        email-address (rf/subscribe [:login/email-address])
        password (rf/subscribe [:login/password])]
    (fn []
      [mui/dialog {:open              (or @open? false)
                   :on-backdrop-click #(rf/dispatch [:turn-off [[:login :show-dialog?]]])
                   :max-width         :xs}
       [mui/dialog-title {:style {:text-align :center}}
        "Zaloguj"]
       [mui/dialog-content
        [flex/vbox {:height          "100%"
                    :justify-content :center
                    :align-items     :center}
         [flex/hbox {:align-items :center}
          [mui/icon {:style {:color @text-secondary}} [:> Email]]
          [mui/form-control
           [mui/input {:placeholder   "adres e-mail"
                       :default-value @email-address
                       :on-change     #(rf/dispatch [:login/set-email-address (u/elem->val %)])
                       :style         {:margin "0px 8px"}}]]] ;TODO
         [flex/hbox {:align-items :center
                     :style       {:margin "16px 0px"}}
          [mui/icon {:style {:color @text-secondary}} [:> Lock]]
          [mui/form-control
           [mui/input {:placeholder   "hasÅ‚o"
                       :default-value @password
                       :type          :password
                       :on-change     #(rf/dispatch [:login/set-password (u/elem->val %)])
                       :style         {:margin "0px 8px"}}]]]
         [mui/button {:variant  :contained
                      :color    :primary
                      :on-click #(rf/dispatch [:login/email-sign-in @email-address @password])
                      :style    {:width "270px"}}
          "zaloguj"]
         [mui/typography {:color   :textSecondary
                          :variant :button
                          :style   {:margin-top "8px"}}     ;TODO
          "lub"]
         (let [fb-theme (mui/create-mui-theme
                          {:palette {:primary {:main "#3b5998"}}})]
           [mui/mui-theme-provider {:theme fb-theme}
            [mui/button {:variant  :contained
                         :color    :primary
                         :on-click #(rf/dispatch [:login/facebook-sign-in])
                         :style    {:width           "270px"
                                    :justify-content :flex-start
                                    :bacground       :red
                                    :margin          "8px 0px"}}
             [:> FacebookBox {:style {:margin-right "24px"}}]
             "zaloguj przez facebook"]])
         (let [g-theme (mui/create-mui-theme
                         {:palette {:primary {:main "#fff"}}})]
           [mui/mui-theme-provider {:theme g-theme}
            [mui/button {:variant  :contained
                         :color    :primary
                         :style    {:width           "270px"
                                    :justify-content :flex-start
                                    :margin          (u/->px (oget g-theme :spacing :unit) 0)}
                         :on-click #(rf/dispatch [:login/google-sign-in])}
             [:img {:src   "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/53/Google_%22G%22_Logo.svg"
                    :style {
                            :height       "18px"
                            :width        "18px"
                            :margin-right "24px"
                            :margin-left  "3px"}}]
             "zaloguj przez Google"]])]]])))
